---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 323
      - text: "老實說，我從沒想過你能做得這麼好。\n力巴爾的勇猛也更加強化了……"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 234
      - text: "「討伐加儂」這個重責大任，\n現在的你應該辦得到吧？"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 257
      - text: "哦？你又來啦？\n是想在討伐災厄加儂前訓練一下嗎？"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 197
      - text: "你對討伐加儂一事感到不安，\n這我也不是不能理解……"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk120:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 261
      - text: "咦？難不成你希望我用這副好嗓子，\n給你一點鼓勵？"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk130:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 236
      - text: "這點我也不是不明白，\n不過有我在一旁守著你，應該就足夠了吧？"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 97
      - text: 你又來啦？
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 264
      - text: "對了……你去過利特村了吧？\n那邊的狀況如何？"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 160
      - text: "從我這裡看過去的樣子，\n大家似乎都過得不錯……"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 235
      - text: "是說，畢竟都過了100年，\n大概已經沒人知道我了吧。"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk240:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 171
      - text: "……不過還是令人在意呢。\n畢竟是故鄉嘛……"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 220
      - text: "你也很努力呢……\n啊，對了。"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 219
      - text: "你救了那位公主之後……\n可不能跟她打聽我的事喔。"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 162
      - text: 不！不管她說了什麼，你都別問！
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk330:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 272
      - text: "畢竟都是100年前的陳年舊事了，\n公主的記憶應該也模糊不清了吧？"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 126
      - text: 你也真纏人……
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 202
      - text: "不過你來得正好，\n我還有件事忘了跟你說……"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 291
      - text: "假如你在某處，\n找到利特族戰士，力巴爾的日記……\n"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 228
      - text: "上面寫的東西全都是胡說八道！\n那些內容可不是我寫的喔！"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk440:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 78
      - text: 知道嗎！？
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 295
      - text: "啊……真是後悔莫及，\n我應該在100年前就跟你切磋一場啊。"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 232
      - text: "出現在利特村的你，跟我來場單挑！\n那肯定……"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 278
      - text: "會成為海拉魯最強騎士，\n對上利特族最強戰士的世紀之戰！"
  Npc_Rito_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 191
      - text: "不管贏也好，輸也好，\n真想跟你一較高下啊……"
